                <h2 class="subheading">Eligibility Criteria</h2>
                <p>To apply online for a driving license, you must meet these eligibility conditions:</p>
                <h3 class="subheading">Learner's License:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>16+ years (for gearless two-wheelers up to 50cc, with parental/guardian consent)</li>
                    <li>18+ years (for motor vehicles with gear (excluding transport vehicles))</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="subheading">Permanent License:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Must hold a valid learner's license for at least 30 days</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="subheading">Commercial License:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Minimum age: 20 years</li>
                    <li>Must have passed Class 8 (varies by state)</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="subheading">General Requirement:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Applicant must be mentally and physically fit to drive</li>
                </ul>

